Installation:
	1) Move to src directory (>>cd [path-to-src])
	2) Compile (>>make all)
	3) Run (>>./assignment1)

User Interaction options:

	ZOOM-IN  			----- +
	ZOOM-OUT 			----- -
	ROTATE Z+	 		----- l
	ROTATE Z-			----- r
	Translate			----- Mouse Left key + drag
	Add Point			----- Mouse left click
	Delete Point	----- Mouse middle click on point to be deleted
	Exit          ----- esc
	

Program Features:

	1) Entire program is built using MVC architecture.

